# Arabic (Ancient) constellation, native: الفرقدان
msgid "The two oryx calves"
msgstr "Los dos terneros oryx"

# Arabic (Ancient) constellation, native: فأس الرحى
msgid "The axe of the grindstone"
msgstr "El hacha de la piedra de afilar"

# Description of Arabic (Ancient) constellation The axe of the grindstone
msgid ""
"Fish shaped two arcs of stars joined at the ends by α UMi and β UMi, named as \n"
"the axe of the grindstone because it revolves around the north stellar pole."
msgstr ""
"Pez en forma de dos arcos de estrellas unidos en los extremos por α UMi y β "
"UMi, llamado así como el hacha de la muela porque gira alrededor del polo "
"norte estelar."

# Arabic (Ancient) constellation, native: بنات نعش
msgid "Daughters of Na'sh"
msgstr "Hijas de Na'sh"

# Description of Arabic (Ancient) constellation Daughters of Na'sh
msgid ""
"The 7 stars of the big dipper, representing 7 girls carrying the bier of their \n"
"father who was killed by Al-Jady (Polaris)."
msgstr ""
"Las 7 estrellas de la Osa Mayor, que representan a 7 niñas que llevan el "
"féretro de su padre asesinado por Al-Jady (Polaris)."

# Arabic (Ancient) constellation, native: القفزة الأولى
msgid "The first leap"
msgstr "el primer salto"

# Description of Arabic (Ancient) constellation The first leap
msgid ""
"The track of the first leap of the gazelles fleeing the nearby lion, represented \n"
"by the two stars: ν UMa and ξ UMa."
msgstr ""
"La huella del primer salto de las gacelas huyendo del cercano león, "
"representada por las dos estrellas: ν UMa y ξ UMa."

# Arabic (Ancient) constellation, native: القفزة الثانية
msgid "The second leap"
msgstr "el segundo salto"

# Description of Arabic (Ancient) constellation The second leap
msgid ""
"The track of the second leap of the gazelles represented by the two stars: λ \n"
"UMa and μ UMa."
msgstr ""
"La huella del segundo salto de las gacelas representada por las dos "
"estrellas: λ UMa y μ UMa."

# Arabic (Ancient) constellation, native: القفزة الثالثة
msgid "The third leap"
msgstr "el tercer salto"

# Description of Arabic (Ancient) constellation The third leap
msgid ""
"The track of the third leap of the gazelles represented by the two stars: ι UMa \n"
"and κ UMa."
msgstr ""
"La huella del tercer salto de las gacelas representada por las dos "
"estrellas: ι UMa y κ UMa."

# Arabic (Ancient) constellation, native: الظباء وأولاد الظباء
msgid "The Gazelles and their youngsters"
msgstr "Las gacelas y sus crías"

# Description of Arabic (Ancient) constellation The Gazelles and their
# youngsters
msgid ""
"An area between Ursa Major and Leo, where the brighter stars are the adult \n"
"gazelles, and the faint stars represent the young ones."
msgstr ""
"Un área entre la Osa Mayor y Leo, donde las estrellas más brillantes son las"
" gacelas adultas y las estrellas débiles representan a las jóvenes."

# Arabic (Ancient) constellation, native: الفارطان
msgid "The two preceding to the water"
msgstr "Los dos que preceden al agua."

# Description of Arabic (Ancient) constellation The two preceding to the water
msgid ""
"The two stars: h UMa and υ UMa, representing two men advancing to the water \n"
"pool to fetch water to help dig the grave of Na'sh, father of Daughters of \n"
"Na'sh."
msgstr ""
"Las dos estrellas: h UMa y υ UMa, representan a dos hombres que avanzan "
"hacia el estanque de agua a buscar agua para ayudar a cavar la tumba de "
"Na'sh, padre de las Hijas de Na'sh."

# Arabic (Ancient) constellation, native: الحوض
msgid "The pool"
msgstr "La piscina"

# Description of Arabic (Ancient) constellation The pool
msgid ""
"An incomplete circle of stars representing a water pool where the gazelles \n"
"drink, and two men are fetching water."
msgstr ""
"Un círculo incompleto de estrellas que representa un estanque de agua donde "
"beben las gacelas, y dos hombres van a buscar agua."

# Arabic (Ancient) constellation, native: أظفار الذئب
msgid "The wolf claws"
msgstr "las garras del lobo"

# Arabic (Ancient) constellation, native: الذئبان
msgid "The two wolves"
msgstr "los dos lobos"

# Description of Arabic (Ancient) constellation The two wolves
msgid ""
"The two stars: f Dra and ω Dra, representing two wolves trying to hunt the \n"
"nearby baby camel, the star HR 6618, surrounded by the four mother camels."
msgstr ""
"Las dos estrellas: f Dra y ω Dra, que representan a dos lobos que intentan "
"cazar al camello bebé cercano, la estrella HR 6618, rodeados por las cuatro "
"madres camellos."

# Arabic (Ancient) constellation, native: العوائذ
msgid "The mother camels"
msgstr "las madres camellos"

# Description of Arabic (Ancient) constellation The mother camels
msgid ""
"An irregular square of four stars, representing four mother camels protecting \n"
"the baby camel, the star HR 6618, from the near by Hyena, the star ι Dra, and \n"
"the two wolves."
msgstr ""
"Un cuadrado irregular de cuatro estrellas, que representa a cuatro madres "
"camellos que protegen al bebé camello, la estrella HR 6618, de la cercana "
"Hiena, la estrella ι Dra y los dos lobos."

# Arabic (Ancient) constellation, native: الأثافي
msgid "The three stone support"
msgstr "El soporte de las tres piedras"

# Description of Arabic (Ancient) constellation The three stone support
msgid ""
"A triangle of three stars representing the stones that are used to hold the \n"
"cooking pot on wood fire."
msgstr ""
"Un triángulo de tres estrellas que representan las piedras que se utilizan "
"para sujetar la olla en el fuego de leña."

# Arabic (Ancient) constellation, native: القدر
msgid "The pot"
msgstr "La olla"

# Description of Arabic (Ancient) constellation The pot
msgid ""
"A circular shape of stars representing a cooking pot near The three stone \n"
"support."
msgstr ""
"Una forma circular de estrellas que representan una olla cerca del soporte "
"de tres piedras."

# Arabic (Ancient) constellation, native: كوكبا الفرق
msgid "The two stars of separation"
msgstr "Las dos estrellas de la separación."

# Arabic (Ancient) constellation, native: الشاء
msgid "The sheep"
msgstr "La oveja"

# Description of Arabic (Ancient) constellation The sheep
msgid ""
"A group of stars representing sheep with the brightest as the shepherd and the \n"
"second brightest as his dog."
msgstr ""
"Un grupo de estrellas representando ovejas con la más brillante como el "
"pastor y la segunda más brillante como su perro."

# Arabic (Ancient) constellation, native: الرمح
msgid "The spear"
msgstr "La lanza"

# Description of Arabic (Ancient) constellation The spear
msgid "The spear of the armed one."
msgstr "La lanza del armado."

# Arabic (Ancient) constellation, native: ذو السلاح
msgid "The armed one"
msgstr "el armado"

# Description of Arabic (Ancient) constellation The armed one
msgid "The star Arcturus representing a man with a spear."
msgstr "La estrella Arcturus representando a un hombre con una lanza."

# Arabic (Ancient) constellation, native: السماك الأعزل
msgid "The unarmed one"
msgstr "el desarmado"

# Description of Arabic (Ancient) constellation The unarmed one
msgid ""
"The star Spica representing a man with no arms as opposed to the armed one."
msgstr ""
"La estrella Spica que representa a un hombre sin brazos en oposición al "
"armado."

# Description of Arabic (Ancient) constellation The hyenas and their
# youngsters
msgid ""
"An area where the brighter stars represent the adult hyenas, and the faint ones \n"
"represent the young ones."
msgstr ""
"Un área donde las estrellas más brillantes representan a las hienas adultas "
"y las débiles representan a las jóvenes."

# Arabic (Ancient) constellation, native: قصعة المساكين
msgid "The bowl of the poor"
msgstr "El plato de los pobres"

# Description of Arabic (Ancient) constellation The bowl of the poor
msgid ""
"The stars of Corona Borealis. The incomplete circle represents a fractured bowl \n"
"of the poor."
msgstr ""
"Las estrellas de Corona Borealis. El círculo incompleto representa un cuenco"
" fracturado de los pobres."

# Arabic (Ancient) constellation, native: النسق الشآمي
msgid "The northern line"
msgstr "la linea del norte"

# Description of Arabic (Ancient) constellation The northern line
msgid ""
"A group of stars arranged in a line that may represent a line of trees at the \n"
"northern side of the desert garden."
msgstr ""
"Un grupo de estrellas dispuestas en una línea que puede representar una "
"hilera de árboles en el lado norte del jardín del desierto."

# Arabic (Ancient) constellation, native: النسق اليماني
msgid "The southern line"
msgstr "la línea sur"

# Description of Arabic (Ancient) constellation The southern line
msgid ""
"Another group of stars arranged in a line that may represent a line of trees at \n"
"the southern side of the desert garden."
msgstr ""
"Otro grupo de estrellas dispuestas en una línea que puede representar una "
"línea de árboles en el lado sur del jardín del desierto."

# Arabic (Ancient) constellation, native: الروضة والأغنام
msgid "The desert garden and the goats"
msgstr "El jardín del desierto y las cabras."

# Description of Arabic (Ancient) constellation The desert garden and the
# goats
msgid ""
"An area of stars representing goats with the brightest stars as the shepherd and \n"
"his two dogs."
msgstr ""
"Un área de estrellas representando cabras con las estrellas más brillantes "
"como el pastor y sus dos perros."

# Description of Arabic (Ancient) constellation The landing eagle
msgid ""
"The bright star Vega with two nearby stars as his wings forming a triangle."
msgstr ""
"La brillante estrella Vega con dos estrellas cercanas como sus alas formando"
" un triángulo."

# Description of Arabic (Ancient) constellation The flying eagle
msgid "The bright star Altair with a star on each side as his spread wings."
msgstr ""
"La estrella brillante Altair con una estrella a cada lado como sus alas "
"extendidas."

# Arabic (Ancient) constellation, native: الفوارس
msgid "The knights"
msgstr "Los Caballeros"

# Description of Arabic (Ancient) constellation The knights
msgid ""
"A line of five stars representing five knights with the star the Rear Knight, \n"
"the bright star Deneb, behind them."
msgstr ""
"Una línea de cinco estrellas que representan a cinco caballeros con la "
"estrella del Caballero Trasero, la estrella brillante Deneb, detrás de "
"ellos."

# Arabic (Ancient) constellation, native: رأس الناقة
msgid "The camel head"
msgstr "la cabeza de camello"

# Arabic (Ancient) constellation, native: عنق الناقة
msgid "The camel neck"
msgstr "el cuello de camello"

# Arabic (Ancient) constellation, native: يدا الناقة
msgid "The camel front legs"
msgstr "Las patas delanteras del camello"

# Arabic (Ancient) constellation, native: الناقة
msgid "The she-camel"
msgstr "la camella"

# Description of Arabic (Ancient) constellation The she-camel
msgid "A group of stars having a shape of a camel."
msgstr "Un grupo de estrellas que tienen forma de camello."

# Description of Arabic (Ancient) constellation The henna tinted hand
msgid "The henna tinted hand of al-Thurayya, the Pleiades."
msgstr "La mano teñida con henna de al-Thurayya, las Pléyades."

# Arabic (Ancient) constellation, native: العاتق
msgid "The shoulder blade"
msgstr "el omoplato"

# Description of Arabic (Ancient) constellation The shoulder blade
msgid "The shoulder blade of al-Thurayya, the Pleiades."
msgstr "El omóplato de al-Thurayya, las Pléyades."

# Arabic (Ancient) constellation, native: المنكب
msgid "The shoulder"
msgstr "El hombro"

# Description of Arabic (Ancient) constellation The shoulder
msgid "The shoulder of al-Thurayya, the Pleiades."
msgstr "El hombro de al-Thurayya, las Pléyades."

# Arabic (Ancient) constellation, native: العضد
msgid "The arm"
msgstr "El brazo"

# Description of Arabic (Ancient) constellation The arm
msgid "The arm of al-Thurayya, the Pleiades."
msgstr "El brazo de al-Thurayya, las Pléyades."

# Arabic (Ancient) constellation, native: المرفق
msgid "The elbow"
msgstr "El codo"

# Description of Arabic (Ancient) constellation The elbow
msgid "The elbow of al-Thurayya, the Pleiades."
msgstr "El codo de al-Thurayya, las Pléyades."

# Arabic (Ancient) constellation, native: الساعد
msgid "The forearm"
msgstr "el antebrazo"

# Description of Arabic (Ancient) constellation The forearm
msgid "The forearm of al-Thurayya, the Pleiades."
msgstr "El antebrazo de al-Thurayya, las Pléyades."

# Arabic (Ancient) constellation, native: الكف الجذماء
msgid "The short hand"
msgstr "la mano corta"

# Description of Arabic (Ancient) constellation The short hand
msgid "The short left hand of al-Thurayya, the Pleiades."
msgstr "La mano izquierda corta de al-Thurayya, las Pléyades."

# Arabic (Ancient) constellation, native: الثريا الصورة
msgid "Al-Thurayya image"
msgstr "Imagen de Al Thurayya"

# Description of Arabic (Ancient) constellation Al-Thurayya image
msgid "An image of a woman with two extended hands"
msgstr "Una imagen de una mujer con dos manos extendidas"

# Arabic (Ancient) constellation, native: العيوق وتوابعه
msgid "Al-Ayyuq and the posts"
msgstr "Al-Ayyuq y los puestos"

# Description of Arabic (Ancient) constellation Al-Ayyuq and the posts
msgid ""
"Al-Ayyuq is the bright star Capella with four bright stars nearby. One is his \n"
"leg, and the three others are the posts."
msgstr ""
"Al-Ayyuq es la estrella brillante Capella con cuatro estrellas brillantes "
"cercanas. Uno es su pierna, y los otros tres son los postes."

# Arabic (Ancient) constellation, native: الخباء الشآمي
msgid "The northern tent"
msgstr "La carpa del norte"

# Arabic (Ancient) constellation, native: القعود
msgid "The young camel"
msgstr "el camello joven"

# Arabic (Ancient) constellation, native: عناق الأرض
msgid "The caracal"
msgstr "el caracal"

# Arabic (Ancient) constellation, native: الكرب - النعام
msgid "The bucket rope knot - The well poles"
msgstr "El nudo de la cuerda del cubo - Los postes del pozo"

# Arabic (Ancient) constellation, native: الفرغ المقدم
msgid "The front bucket mouth"
msgstr "La boca del cubo delantero"

# Arabic (Ancient) constellation, native: الفرغ المؤخر
msgid "The rear bucket mouth"
msgstr "La boca del cubo trasero"

# Arabic (Ancient) constellation, native: الرشاء
msgid "The well bucket rope"
msgstr "La cuerda del balde del pozo"

# Arabic (Ancient) constellation, native: الحوت
msgid "The fish"
msgstr "El pescado"

# Arabic (Ancient) constellation, native: الدلو
msgid "The well bucket"
msgstr "el balde del pozo"

# Arabic (Ancient) constellation, native: الأيبسان
msgid "The two forelegs of the lamb"
msgstr "Las dos patas delanteras del cordero."

# Arabic (Ancient) constellation, native: الشرطان
msgid "The two signs"
msgstr "los dos signos"

# Arabic (Ancient) constellation, native: البطين
msgid "The little abdomen"
msgstr "El pequeño vientre"

# Arabic (Ancient) constellation, native: الثريا
msgid "Al-Thurayya"
msgstr "Al Thurayya"

# Description of Arabic (Ancient) constellation Al-Thurayya
msgid ""
"The Pleiades, imagined as a woman loved by al-Dabaran, the bright star \n"
"Aldebaran."
msgstr ""
"Las Pléyades, imaginadas como una mujer amada por al-Dabarán, la brillante "
"estrella Aldebarán."

# Arabic (Ancient) constellation, native: الحمل
msgid "The lamb"
msgstr "El cordero"

# Description of Arabic (Ancient) constellation The lamb
msgid ""
"A group of stars in the same region of Aries but includes the Pleiades as the \n"
"fatty tail of the lamb."
msgstr ""
"Un grupo de estrellas en la misma región de Aries pero incluye a las "
"Pléyades como la cola gorda del cordero."

